# Review

## Verdict

One of: **Approved** · **Approved with comments** · **Rejected**

Reject on any gate failure — no deferred blockers. Non-trivial changes need `dotnet build`, `dotnet test`, verification notes.

## Gates

| Gate | Skill |
|------|-------|
| Validation | `/validation` |
| Mapping | `/mapping` |
| Logging | `/logging` |
| Persistence | `/persistence` |
| Security | `/security` |
| Data access | `/repository` `/ef` |
| Refactor safety | `/refactor` |

Feature PRs: trace one write + one read path. Frontend: loading/error/empty on async boundaries.

## Reject when

Build/test fail · skill reports Fail · DbContext in Application · stubs/disabled tests · N+1/unbounded list · missing auth on protected endpoints

Blockers: `file:line` + fix. Workflow: `workflows/code-review.md`
